==Heads==
Early:
*Leontius (fl. 1123-1126)
*Cyril (fl. 1141<U+2013>1143)
*Euthemius (fl. 1170)
*Kalinik (fl. 1196)
Since the resurrection of the Serbian Patriarchate in 1920:
*[[Mihajlo <U+0160>iljak]] (1920<U+2014>1928)
*[[Serafim Jovanovi<U+0107>]] (1928<U+2014>1945)
*[[Vladimir Raji<U+0107>]] (1945<U+2014>1956)
*[[Pavle Stoj<U+010D>evi<U+0107>]] (1957<U+2014>1990)
*[[Artemije Radosavljevi<U+0107>]] (1991<U+2014>2010)
*[[Atanasije Jevti<U+0107>]] (2010)
*[[Amfilohije Radovi<U+0107>]] (2010)
*[[Teodosije <U+0160>ibali<U+0107>]] (2010-)

